high_descs: Turn left for two steps, turn right and face the counter, looking up at the towel ring.
Take the white towel from the towel ring.
Bring the towel down and turn right for three steps, turn left for two steps, turn left and face the counter.
Put the towel on the counter, near the front center, standing up with the two ends on the bottom.
Turn left for three steps, turn right for six steps, turn right to face the counter and look up at the towel ring.
Take the white towel from the towel ring.
Bring the towel down and turn right for seven steps, take a left for two steps, turn left and face the counter.
Put the towel over the standing towel already on the counter, covering it completely.
anns.task_desc: Put two towels standing on the counter, with one over the other.

high_descs: Look up to face the towel hanging on the wall.
Pick up the towel hanging on the wall.
Step right to face the right end of the sink.
Place the towel on the right end of the sink.
Step left to face the towel hanging on the wall.
Pick up the towel hanging on the wall.
Step right to face the right end of the sink.
Place the towel on the right end of the sink.
anns.task_desc: To move two towels from the wall to the right side of the sink.

high_descs: Turn left and walk forward, then turn right and walk up to the counter and look up at the wall.
Take the wash cloth off of the metal ring that is on the wall to the right of the mirror.
Walk over to the right end of the counter.
Put the wash cloth on the counter.
Turn left and walk towards the shower, then turn turn left and walk over to the wall and turn right.
Take the wash cloth off of the metal ring that is on the wall to the left of the mirror.
Walk back over to the right end of the counter.
Put the wash cloth on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Move two wash cloths to the counter.
